---
title: Garlicky Lamb Rissoles & Cheesy Wedges with Cucumber Salad & Herby Mayo
description: Lamb mince can raise rissoles to number one in our dinner time charts. They are the fan fave when you can dip them in a herby mayo. The secret to fame for this dish is melting Parmesan cheese over golden wedges.

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving.*
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/6753cc3c4d01175c884ecb19-80d3f21c.jpeg
